\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
iBUGS
\series default
 is an R package which aims to make it easier to call WinBUGS and OpenBUGS
 in R.
 The computation is done by 
\series bold
R2WinBUGS
\series default
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
