\series bold
gWidgetsRGtk2
\series default
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "gWidgetsRGtk2"

\end_inset

.
 To start the GUI, simply type 
\family typewriter
library(iBUGS)
\family default
 in R.
 In case you close the window carelessly, you may start it again by 
\family typewriter
